Notes on Nginx
============

#### Installing Nginx on Ubuntu

The latest version available is Nginx 1.6.0, but it is only avaiable via PPA. To 
install, add the PPA to your system, update your local repository index and install
the Nginx package:

    sudo add-apt-repository ppa:nginx/stable

    sudo apt-get update

    sudo apt-get install nginx


#### Removing Nginx

Optionally, to remove Nginx:

    sudo apt-get remove nginx
    
    
#### Commands

Command line [options]( http://wiki.nginx.org/CommandLine ).
